{"tid":2094862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「保就業」計劃50%補貼, 繼續8折出糧, 呢類腦細正仆街","createTime":"2020-07-05T04:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T10:36:00.000Z","uid":142878,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ab6bdde2e149aed8ce531fb3ff8be39e42667b","tid":2094862,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"我聽到有幾個朋友做律師樓<br />\n個d腦細真係好仆街<br />\n已經拎緊政府個「保就業」計劃<br />\n但繼續8折出糧<br />\n<br />\n呢個腦細真係好醒, 50%政府出, 自己出30%人工<br />\n但D員工要做100-120%工作量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n炒咗幾個全職員工<br />\n請返幾個每星期返1/2日ge part time<br />\n又賺一大筆<br />\n當個全職18,000一個月, 腦細袋咗9,000<br />\n個part time 1個月開工4日, 頂多咪3,000<br />\n一個就賺咗6,000<br />\n<br />\n其實可以再仆街d ga wo<br />\n全部炒晒, 再請返一堆自己人扮出糧<br />\n位位9,000袋袋平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咩叫人面獸心<br />\n我諗就係呢d人啦<br />\n法律ge野, 點夠你玩呀, 律師腦細"},{"pid":"53a677fc530f5b26983eaeb301975b739c22b6a8","tid":2094862,"uid":142878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:29:04.000Z","msg":"不過可以再仆街d<br />\n由於公司d生意大跌咗一半<br />\n所以本公司決定5折出糧<br />\n<br />\n正到爆啦<br />\n一蚊都唔洗畀<br />\n就有班傻仔日日幫你打工3個月 (6-8月)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6473d72d8a0941e20522d86c5594f4f744ac7a7","tid":2094862,"uid":217990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:35:08.000Z","msg":"我都半價出緊糧啦<br />\n即係只收政府俾個一半補貼咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d4932a74e9f20b07dd7cbda3aec1fc66cfa379","tid":2094862,"uid":142878,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c6473d72d8a0941e20522d86c5594f4f744ac7a7","tid":2094862,"uid":217990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:35:08.000Z","msg":"我都半價出緊糧啦<br />\n即係只收政府俾個一半補貼咋<img src=